item.title: Oh Shenandoah
item.description: 1. Oh Shenandoah, I long to see you Away you rolling river. Oh Shenandoah, I long to see you Away, we’re bound away ‘cross the wide Missouri 2. Oh Shenandoah, I love your daughter Away you rolling river Oh Shenandoah, I love your daughter Away, we’re bound away ‘cross the wide Missouri 3. Tis seven years, since I last saw thee Away you rolling river Tis seven years, since I last saw thee
